"{\"uid\": \"today.com-news-olympics-gymnastics-team-final-gold-usa-rcna164326\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Ariana Brockington  Trending News Reporter  Anna Kaplan  News and Trending Reporter  Less than 24 hours after theU.S.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"score\": 0.9999999939873305, \"rank\": 6.012473573971586e-09, \"text\": \"Michael Kors\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kaplan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Kaplan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kaplan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kaplan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"women's gymnastics team won the gold medalat the 2024 Paris Olympics, Jade Carey and Hezly Rivera still can not quite believe their realities.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999995814906436, \"rank\": 4.178568881060757e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carey, who competed in Tokyo in 2021, reflected on what the team's win meant to her on TODAY on Wednesday, July 31.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551103184296329e-28, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999926914208283, \"rank\": 7.306186345103265e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It just feels so incredible,\\\" Carey said.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551103184296329e-28, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super excited and super proud of this team and everything that we have overcome to get back here and on top of the podium again.\\\"\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rivera, sitting next to Carey, also shared what it was like to be a part of the winning team.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999995814906436, \"rank\": 4.178568881060757e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551103184296329e-28, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's so surreal being here with (this) amazing group of girls,\\\" Rivera said.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999995814906436, \"rank\": 4.178568881060757e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud of this team and everything that we have worked so hard for.\\\"\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carey and Rivera, along with Simone Biles, Suni Lee and Jordan Chiles, topped the podium in the team final on July 30, marking the first time the women's gymnastics team has won gold since their victory at the 2016 Rio Olympics.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551103184296329e-28, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999995814906436, \"rank\": 4.178568881060757e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Rivera, 16,competing on Team USAwith Biles was a full-circle moment after meeting the gymnast when she was just 7 years old.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999995814906436, \"rank\": 4.178568881060757e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never would have thought that would happen, being on the same team as Simone,\\\" she said while on TODAY.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always looked up to her and just not even just competing with her, but training with her as well, has been such an amazing experience, and I am so blessed to be a part of his team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carey appeared to have recovered from anillness she experienced last week, which she previously said affected her performance in the women's gymnastics qualification rounds on Sunday, July 28.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551103184296329e-28, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old competed in the vault at the team finals, and she shared with TODAY co-anchors Savannah Guthrie and Hoda Kotb what was going through her mind before the event.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Savannah Guthrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\"}, {\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was just telling myself to be my normal self that I am every day in the gym, that I have done so much work and that I knew how to do it and it would all be over in 10 seconds,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of pressure on that one vault, but I knew that if I was just my normal self that it would get the job done for what the team needed.\\\"\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was - Carey, Chiles and Biles shined on the vault, setting the team up to deliver thrilling performances on the uneven bars, balance beam and floor.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA entered the final event, the floor exercise, with a slight lead of 3.602 points.\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9996476734585642, \"rank\": 0.0003514812683374487, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, Lee and Chiles then executed nearly flawless routines that cemented Team USA's victory.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999928654688, \"rank\": 6.876510693792366e-09, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9996476734585642, \"rank\": 0.0003514812683374487, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee scored 13.533, improving on her qualifying round score of 13.100, while Chiles received 13.966.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2602, \"end\": 2605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999928654688, \"rank\": 6.876510693792366e-09, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was the final Team USA gymnast to complete her floor routine.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2722, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9996476734585642, \"rank\": 0.0003514812683374487, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She flipped and twisted around as Taylor Swift's \\\"...Ready For It?\\\"\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"blasted.\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ladies held up the American flag, smiled wide and jumped up and down to celebrate when it was revealed that they won gold.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2872, \"end\": 2885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999971832949, \"rank\": 2.8168943189595296e-09, \"text\": \"American flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The win came after Team USA started the day off strong.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9996476734585642, \"rank\": 0.0003514812683374487, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chiles kicked things off by showing off her skills on the uneven bars.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Analyst and gymnast Laurie Hernandez praised Chiles' performance as \\\"one of the best routines\\\" she could've mastered.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory also means Biles became the USA gymnast with themost Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3263, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6112994868564031, \"rank\": 0.6345593285647495, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was previously tied with\\u00a0\\\"Magnificent Seven\\\" star Shannon Miller, who has seven Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.887178660128617e-60, \"text\": \"Shannon Miller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chiles later fell on the beam at the start of her routine but recovered and finished strong.\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then Lee and Biles had their turns on the beam and wowed the audience, including Savannah and Hoda.\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3503, \"end\": 3506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999928654688, \"rank\": 6.876510693792366e-09, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 3579, \"end\": 3587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_River\", \"score\": 0.9942348341240036, \"rank\": 0.005435286316126095, \"text\": \"Savannah\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_River\"}, {\"begin\": 3592, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"score\": 0.5202438276363072, \"rank\": 0.6999999999999931, \"text\": \"Hoda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, who overcame acalf injury, once again proved that she is unmatched in the sport by avoiding a fall on the beam and posting a 14.733.\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Lee, Chiles and Biles' floor routines - in which Chiles nearly burst into tears after her impressive performance - Team USA ended the final with a score of\\u00a0171.296.\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999928654688, \"rank\": 6.876510693792366e-09, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy\\u00a0came in second place and\\u00a0Brazil\\u00a0will receive the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3911, \"end\": 3916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999733887683039, \"rank\": 2.3734287684929583e-05, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", 